Clerics who take the Pestilence domain seek to spread death and decay, and are granted spells that further such dolorous desires.

<b>Domain Special Ability and Bonus Spells</b>
- Divine Health: The cleric is immune to the diseases they seek to spread among the world.

- The cleric gains access to the following spells at the specified spell level: <i>Contagion (2), Poison (3), Scourge (7), Horrid Wilting(8)</i>.